OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFine, with
OL,6,Fevening sunny spells giving way to
OL,7,Fclear periods. Colder than the
OL,8,Fprevious night given light winds and
OL,9,Flittle cloud cover, with a widespread
OL,10,Ffrost developing, especially in prone
OL,11,Frural spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FAfter a clear and cold start,
OL,14,Fcloud increasing from the northwest,
OL,15,Fbringing a little rain at times during
OL,16,Fthe afternoon. Becoming drier,
OL,17,Fbrighter and breezier into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
