OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FChangeable and rather cool. Rain or
OL,7,Fshowers at times, but some drier
OL,8,Fspells too, especially later in the
OL,9,Fweek, with lighter winds by this time.
OL,10,FFurther slight frosts possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
